OL,3,CDriver who killed 'good Samaritan'
OL,4,Cguilty of murder
OL,6,FA driver who killed a "good Samaritan"
OL,7,Fas he tended to a woman lying in the
OL,8,Froad after a wedding day brawl has
OL,9,Fbeen found guilty of murder.
OL,11,FHassan Jhangur, 25, ploughed into a
OL,12,Fcrowd of people, including Chris
OL,13,FMarriott, in Burngreave, Sheffield,
OL,14,Fafter a family feud erupted into
OL,15,Fviolence.
OL,17,FFather-of-two Mr Marriott, 46, who had
OL,18,Fstopped to help Jhangur's own sister
OL,19,Fas she lay injured in College Court,
OL,20,Fdied from his injuries.
