OL,3,CDriver who killed 'good Samaritan'
OL,4,Cguilty of murder
OL,6,FPolice described him as a "good
OL,7,FSamaritan" who had paid for his
OL,8,Fkindness with his life.
OL,10,FJurors heard four others were also
OL,11,Fhurt in the incident, including off-
OL,12,Fduty midwife Alison Norris, who had
OL,13,Falso gone to help, and Jhangur's own
OL,14,Fmother and sister.
OL,16,FJhangur, of Whiteways Road, Sheffield,
OL,17,Fthen got out of the car and stabbed
OL,18,Fhis new brother-in-law, Hasan Khan,
OL,19,Fseveral times.
