OL,3,CDriver who killed 'good Samaritan'
OL,4,Cguilty of murder
OL,6,FHe admitted causing Mr Marriott's
OL,7,Fdeath by dangerous driving but denied
OL,8,Fmurder and manslaughter.
OL,10,FThe jury at a retrial found him guilty
OL,11,Fby a majority verdict following 18
OL,12,Fhours of deliberations.
OL,14,FA jury at a previous trial had failed
OL,15,Fto reach a verdict.
OL,17,FSheffield Crown Court heard the
OL,18,Fincident happened after the wedding of
OL,19,FJhangur's sister Amaani and Hasan Khan
OL,20,Fon 27 December 2023.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/7
