OL,3,CDriver who killed 'good Samaritan'
OL,4,Cguilty of murder
OL,6,FA feud between the couple's families
OL,7,Ferupted into a brawl when the bride's
OL,8,Fmother, Ambreen, and sister, Nafeesa,
OL,9,Farrived outside the Khan family home.
OL,11,FMr Marriott, a charity worker, was on
OL,12,Fa walk with his wife, Bryony, and two
OL,13,Fyoung sons when he came across Nafeesa
OL,14,FKhan lying in the road and went to
OL,15,Fhelp her shortly before Jhangur
OL,16,Fcollided with him in his Seat Ibiza
OL,17,Fcar.
