OL,3,CDriver who killed 'good Samaritan'
OL,4,Cguilty of murder
OL,6,FJhangur was found guilty of causing
OL,7,Ffour others grievous bodily harm with
OL,8,Fintent.
OL,10,FHe was acquitted of the attempted
OL,11,Fmurder of Hasan Khan but guilty of
OL,12,Fwounding him with intent.
OL,14,FHis father, Mohammed Jhangur, 57, of
OL,15,FWhiteways Road, Sheffield, was found
OL,16,Fguilty of perverting the course of
OL,17,Fjustice after he concealed a knife.
OL,19,FMr Justice Morris told Jhangur he
OL,20,Ffaces a life sentence.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/7
